<h3 data-sourcepos="41:1-41:7" dir="auto">
<a id="user-content-pwd" class="anchor" href="#pwd" aria-hidden="true"></a>pwd</h3>
<p data-sourcepos="43:1-43:225" dir="auto">Now that we know what is around us, we need to know where we are to do that we can use<code>pwd</code> if the shell prompt doesn't let you know your location already. <code>pwd</code> takes no arguments and simply prints the current path and exits</p>
