<h3 data-sourcepos="63:1-63:8" dir="auto">
<a id="user-content-sudo" class="anchor" href="#sudo" aria-hidden="true"></a>sudo</h3>
<p data-sourcepos="65:1-65:208" dir="auto"><code>sudo</code> can precede most commands on this list and gives you access to the system as the root user  temporarily, you may have to use root priveleges when installing packages from your distro package repository</p>
