<h3 data-sourcepos="85:1-85:6" dir="auto">
<a id="user-content-cp" class="anchor" href="#cp" aria-hidden="true"></a>cp</h3>
<p data-sourcepos="87:1-87:204" dir="auto">This is the terminal version of copy and all you have to do is pass the source and destination file to the program, i.e. <code>cp &lt;source&gt; &lt;destination&gt;</code>, this will copy the source file to the destination file</p>
