<a id="user-content-mv" class="anchor" href="#mv" aria-hidden="true"></a>mv</h3>
<p data-sourcepos="93:1-93:180" dir="auto"><code>mv</code> is similar to <code>cp</code> but it moves the source file to the destination location, it could also be considered a renaming tool because renaming is equivalent to moving to a new name</p>
